.auth-card 
    .auth-card__title
        span Регистрация
    .auth-card__fields 
        div.d-flex.align-center
            | !{firstNameTextField}
            | !{lastNameTextField}
        | !{emailTextField}
        div.d-flex.align-center
            | !{phoneTextField}
            | !{usernameTextField}
        div.d-flex.align-center
            | !{passwordTextField}
            | !{passwordRepeatTextField}
    .auth-card__actions
        | !{button}
        .additional
            a(href="#" id="has-account-link") Уже есть аккаунт?
            